<item>
            <title>[LU-9239] replay-single test_15: Restart of mds1 failed!</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9239</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/52027924-0a4d-11e7-b5b2-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/52027924-0a4d-11e7-b5b2-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This looks identical to ATM-188:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;from test_log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: trevis-44vm3 mkdir -p /mnt/lustre-mds1; mount -t lustre -o loop /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1 /mnt/lustre-mds1
trevis-44vm3: mount: /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1: failed to setup loop device: No such file or directory
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However, after looking more closely at the &quot;failover to&quot; MDS (vm3), it appears that it wasn&apos;t ready to takeover for the &quot;failover from&quot; MDS (vm7):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;last line in vm3&apos;s dmesg:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Key type id_legacy registered
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;dmesg lines from a healthy server:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Key type id_legacy registered
device-mapper: uevent: version 1.0.3
device-mapper: ioctl: 4.34.0-ioctl (2015-10-28) initialised: dm-devel@redhat.com
EXT4-fs (dm-9): mounting ext3 file system using the ext4 subsystem
EXT4-fs (dm-9): recovery complete
EXT4-fs (dm-9): mounted filesystem with ordered data mode. Opts: (null
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Followed by numerous &quot;Lustre:&quot; messages.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>trevis-44vm1 thru 8, Failover test, &lt;br/&gt;
RHEL7.3/ldiskfs, branch master, v2.9.53.19.gdad9ce4, b3534&lt;br/&gt;
</environment>
